{"tid":403483,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 硬件成本曝光","createTime":"2017-09-17T08:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T10:09:05.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5095b1c80e665be01ca3081f42b473dc9d0789aa","tid":403483,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:43:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">號稱是史上最貴的 iPhone 手機，它到底貴在哪裡呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/screenshot_995b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fscreenshot_995b.jpg&h=6adf5950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期有媒體爆料了 iPhone X 的硬件成本，其總體硬件成本高達 412.75美元，相比起 iPhone 7 的總硬件成本為 224.8 美元，幾乎高出整整一倍。據瞭解，iPhone X 最貴部分是採購自 Samsung 的 5.8 吋 OLED 屏幕，成本達 80 美元，其餘：<br />\n<br />\n觸控成本為 15 美元，<br />\nCPU成本為 26 美元，<br />\n基帶射頻成本為 18 美元，<br />\n無線成本為 8.75 美元，<br />\nDRAM 成本為 24 美元，<br />\nNAND 成本為 45 美元，<br />\nPA 等成本為 8 美元，<br />\n3D 鏡頭成本為 25 美元，<br />\n模擬器件成本為 9.5 美元，<br />\n音頻解碼器成本為 2.5 美元，<br />\n鏡頭成本為 33 美元，<br />\n電池成本為 9 美元，<br />\n無線充電接收端成本為 6 美元，<br />\nPCB 成本為 15 美元，<br />\n聲學成本為 12 美元，<br />\nHaptics成本為 1 0 美元，<br />\n外觀件總計 53 美元，<br />\n雙面玻璃成本為 18 美元，<br />\n不鏽鋼中框成本為 35 美元，<br />\n射頻天線成本為  5 美元<br />\n其他配件成本為 8 美元，各項合計相加為 412.7 5美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/09/16/iphone-x-price/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2Fiphone-x-price%2F&d=9ulIGd%2B19GD%2FoCX6EKh8F54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=cd1724f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/09/16/iphone-x-price/</a></div>"},{"pid":"2031788b444a885912964bbe60a4b4d0ecedafbe","tid":403483,"uid":63,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"研究費 軟件費用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba7b73523b0b3c0972004afee848232800e8478","tid":403483,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:46:31.000Z","msg":"食足200% <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d3784c158250b0e2090f2094a7e7165949b374","tid":403483,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"貴在 R&amp;D"},{"pid":"7ec620a5f96ff7d8c36ccfb37d1236843a8e8974","tid":403483,"uid":33190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究費 軟件費用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心，都真係幾高成本下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果計埋宣傳，back up同維修，真係唔算賺好多"},{"pid":"f9b69a4ff99b3973fc0a9e94eb6b06d080a0ea11","tid":403483,"uid":294,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:51:08.000Z","msg":"五香肉丁麵成本曝光<br />\n<br />\n號稱是史上最貴的早餐，它到底貴在哪裡呢？<br />\n<br />\n五香肉丁5分1罐, 3元 ,<br />\n普通即食麵 1.5元, <br />\n湯底 0.5元<br />\n其他配料成本為 0.3元，各項合計相加為5.3元。"},{"pid":"54ad497d5f4ddcd6d38f9d56b61f9a648bf5c844","tid":403483,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"請班藍精靈唔駛錢咩"},{"pid":"e15d4a48d4f0ea9578f90b73cc0dde13e1311f09","tid":403483,"uid":55374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"個成本價係面嗰浸<br />\n大量生產個價可以更低"},{"pid":"64aa1a701668967b4c9ca5590c92815ce54f2f26","tid":403483,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"我出夠1000美金，唔知除左apple有邊個可以砌到一部iphone x出黎？"},{"pid":"5232a5d7d449c47a1063316a02e9d5e778d6675e","tid":403483,"uid":55374,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我出夠1000美金，唔知除左apple有邊個可以砌到一部iphone x出黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\niphone貴在軟件上"},{"pid":"f1c6f40afdd48f9967c1816